&lt;h2&gt;Discharge Planning Assistant&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The discharge planning team are looking for an enthusiastic individual to join their team.The discharge planning assistant role will be based on the ward working alongside the ward team supporting and educating the staff with all processes relating to discharge ensuring they happen in a safe and timely manner.You will be collaboratively working at times alongside multi professional agencies.You will be expected manage a case-load of patients to facilitate safe and timely discharges from the acute setting ensuring and support required is in place.We will provide an induction programme for the successful candidate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 13/11/2020&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
